We have recommended that the Municipality:

Expedite the implementation of its 20% Development Projects in order to provide its constituents of the benefits due them;

Comply with Sections 9 & 10 of Annex E of the Revised IRR of RA 9184 and the Manual on the Procurement of Infrastructure Projects in granting suspension of works and extension of contract times to achieve the timely implementation of its 20% Development Projects.

